| Repo | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `omniclaude` | Claude Code plugin — hooks, skills, agents |
| `omnibase_core` | Core runtime, Pydantic models, contracts, validators |
| `omnibase_infra` | Infrastructure services — session, config store, Kafka |
| `omnidash` | Next.js analytics dashboard |
| `omniintelligence` | Intelligence nodes — intent, drift, review |
| `omnimemory` | Document ingestion and semantic retrieval |
| `omninode_infra` | API service, Kubernetes manifests, Terraform |

